WHITE, Respondent, v. NEW YORK, L. E. & W. R. CO., Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Mary M. White, administratrix, etc., against the New York, Lake Erie & Western Railroad Company.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment and order affirmed, with costs.
